title: Greek Lamb Pita Sandwich with Easter Leftovers ! Gyros γύρος !
description:
Fluffy bread, yogurt sauce (tzatziki) and marinated Lamb in this delicious yet so simple sandwich. And we use Easter Leftovers to make it. What else ?

Special shout out to all the Greek people in the French Guy Cooking community. Kalimera ! Ef karisto !
